ygData.subject: Re: [eqbards] Selo's Consonant Chain
ygData.msgSnippet: It s been like this for me since we started getting the message that it wears off.  Nothing seemed different as of this latest patch.  It was so bad for me
ygData.messageBody:
It's been like this for me since we started getting the message that it
wears off. Nothing seemed different as of this latest patch. It was so bad
for me over the weekend against the Dino in OOT that I was resigned to only
playing chains. I can understand having high resists, but I did not know
mobs got secondary resists as a part of this song.

Darkfox Reven'tsol
Xegony


> I used three different times yesterday. Once prepatch (couldn't sleep)
and
> twice afterwards. All three times used it nearly continuously for over 2
> hrs. Post patch it was wearing off early on greens about 30% of the time.
> Never had seen it wear off early on a green pre patch. Will be using it
> again tonite and should get more results, but it certainly looks like a
nerf
> to me.
>
> Kit
